# bayesian-forecasting needs NO API key: Binance public klines are free and keyless.
# This file exists for consistency with the other repos in the handbook, some of which
# do need keys (Etherscan, FRED, Anthropic). Copy to .env and edit only if you want to
# point at a different Binance base URL (e.g. a regional mirror).

# BINANCE_BASE_URL=https://api.binance.com
